@section questions Questions, Issues and Contributions

If you have any questions, issues or suggestions, please feel free to open an issue or a PR directly 
on [GitHub](https://github.com/Thoemi09/simplemc).

Every bug report, feature request or contribution is highly appreciated and will be reviewed as soon 
as possible.
